snippet.title: Two Surprising Fibonacci Puzzles (TANTON: Mathematics)
snippet.description: Here are two very different puzzles that seem to connect with the Fibonacci numbers in a surprising way: The language of ABEEBA and ordered parition numbers. This video just states and plays with the puzzles. The answer video gives the answers!
